  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You pour chakra into your weapon as it fires, so much that it shatters as it flies, dealing damage over a wide area. Select a 20-foot radius area. Hostile Creatures in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save they take 4d6 damage of your weapons type and gain a rank of Dazzled as the explosion throws them off balance.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For every rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost by 3 and the damage of both attack and save by 1d8.</p>",
