      "description": "<p><strong>Max Ranks:</strong> 5</p><p>• A <strong>Dazzled</strong> creatures eyes become overloaded with flashes of colors, gaining a -2 penalty to all checks that rely on sight for each rank it has. • A <strong>Dazzled</strong> creature suffers a -2 penalty to attack rolls for each rank it has and cannot gain advantage on Ranged attack rolls.</p><p>• A <strong>Dazzled</strong> creature reduced the range of Jutsu's cast and ranged attacks made by 15 feet for each rank it has down to a minimum of 5 feet.</p><p>• A <strong>Dazzled</strong> creature can make a DC 15 Constitution ability check as an action, to remove all ranks of this condition.</p>",
